videos.description: Greg Tucker maintains possession and drains an and-1 jumper.
videos.headline: Greg Tucker puts up an and-1 jumper

videos.description: Chandler Rowe coming in clutch with the huge block.
videos.headline: Chandler Rowe with the rejection

videos.description: Erik Durham jukes out Matthew Butler and makes a three pointer to add to the Gamecocks lead.
videos.headline: Erik Durham gets Matthew Butler to jump and drains a 3-pointer

videos.description: Norbertas Giga slams it down and draws the UT-Martin defender to foul Giga.
videos.headline: Norbertas Giga puts defender on the poster and draws the foul

videos.description: The Gamecocks of Jacksonville State defeats UT-Martin 66-55 to win their conference and a bid to the NCAA tournament.
videos.headline: Jacksonville State punches ticket to the tournament
